Default Host File

/etc/ansible/hosts

Customer Host File

ansible-playbook -i customer/host.file

INI Based Host File Examples

# This is ungrouped
mail.doruk.net.tr

# This is grouped
[hostingservers]
web1.dorukcloud.com
web2.dorukcloud.com

Or give an alias and set ip of each

[mailservers]
mail1	ansible_ssh_host=x.x.y.y
mail2	ansible_ssh_host=t.t.r.r
